==English==
===Etymology===
Old English ''[[starian]]''

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɛə(r)|-ɛə(r)]]

===Homophones===
*[[stair]]

===Verb===
'''stare''' ([[stares]], [[stared]], [[staring]]

# [[look]] fixedly

===Noun===
'''stare''' (pl. ''stares'')

# a persistent [[gaze]]

